text:
Hey hey, Fuyuko-chan, which one would you choose!?
Which one suits me better, huh~!?

Haha, you're so lively.
What's up?

Seems like she's struggling
to choose new clothes~!
What kind of clothes are they?
Isn't it the one on the right?
I think the left one is better.

This one, this one! Producer, take a look~!
Then tell me which one's better~?

It's a big responsibility,
so choose carefully, okay?

Oh my, don't just peek at people's
phones without permission.

Eh!? Ah, I did it without thinking!!
Sorry...!

Okay!
Then the left one it is~â™ª
